{"tid":2022581,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Intel Core i5-10400 CPU 賣街 HK$1,499","createTime":"2020-05-18T11:51:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T00:38:00.000Z","uid":104804,"like":12,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"af9db96709c67efe679c1e283c0bdd375b9e753c","tid":2022581,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T11:51:58.000Z","msg":"仲有兩日 Intel 第 10 代 Core 處理器開始賣街啦，貧僧收到風 Core i5-10400 CPU 賣街 HK$1,499，6 核心、12 線程、12MB L3 Cache，核心時脈 2.9GHz Base Clock、最高 4.3GHz Boost Clock，最高 TDP 65W。<br />\n個價同舊代 Core i5-9400 同價，但追加左 Hyper-Threading 技術，Turbo Boost 高左 200MHz 仲有多左 3MB Cache，性價比真係高咗好多，唯一係轉左新 LGA1200，舊 MB唔支援果「撠撠」哋。<br />\nIntel Core i5-9400  (2.9~4.1GHz 6C / 6T 9MB L3) HK$1,499<br />\nIntel Core i5-10400 (2.9~4.3GHz 6C / 12T 12MB L3) HK$1,499 📌<br />\nAMD Ryzen 5 3600 (3.6~4.2GHz 6C/ 12T 32MB L3) HK$1,570<br />\n<br />\n連登仔點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3600定10400"},{"pid":"5fe5c047682a75c950768ead9ec0929fc113ea12","tid":2022581,"uid":343361,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T11:55:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">AMD yes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"23be84483e0a806a23346d98ae5639fd3e544b12","tid":2022581,"uid":1518,"like":21,"dislike":4,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T12:00:02.000Z","msg":"買intel正on9"},{"pid":"a67f6e130a6a7b556c9afe98c847f46804d10ddd","tid":2022581,"uid":43369,"like":39,"dislike":5,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T12:01:25.000Z","msg":"連登仔：amd yes!<br />\n轉個頭買intel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00748ad62b3c411574770bded09b182db98c8a8","tid":2022581,"uid":45189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T12:05:16.000Z","msg":"係都10400F"},{"pid":"8c28717f588c0c2876d83317781a3a6e43b6a676","tid":2022581,"uid":79829,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyT